data.description: Welcome home to 307 Easy Rock, conveniently located near Highway 90, across from Zoosiana.  This traditional style home features white vertical hardiplank, two car garage and easy to maintain landscaping, plus curb appeal!  The interior exhibits a white palette with dark accents, trey ceilings, recessed lighting,  transom windows, tall ceilings, open  and split floor plan design, a second  story,  and sandstone wood flooring throughout.  The paneled gas burning fireplace with mantle, takes the show in the living area.  The kitchen is complete with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a wet island with seating, coffee nook, and a walk-in pantry. Decompress in your oversized master suite complemented by a trey ceiling, spa-like bathroom, decorated in shiplap, dual vanities, soaking tub,  and large master closet.  Enjoy entertaining in your privately fenced in back-yard, under your covered patio and outdoor kitchen. Schedule your tour today!
